name: Failure At The Cave
Lore: '''That place is strong with the dark side of the Force. A domain of evil it is. In you must go.''',
Text: 'Deploy on Dagobah: Cave. Target an apprentice on Dagobah. All Jedi Test game text is suspended. If target present during any battle phase, opponent draws destiny. If destiny < 4, you retrieve 2 Force (also, if destiny = 0, target is lost). Otherwise, Utinni Effect canceled.',
